                        <interp inst="t18480403-name-322" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES BURNS.</persName>
                  </hi> This order is not my writing—I do not know the pri<lb></lb>soner—I never saw him before—I never gave him this order, or authorised him or any one to write it.</p>
